# 🖥️ 1. Windows Demo – Outlook Not Opening

## 🎯 Scenario
User reports:
> “Outlook won’t open. It just hangs on the loading screen.”

## 🔧 Troubleshooting Steps (Demo)
1. Check Task Manager → Outlook running in background  
2. End all Outlook processes  
3. Run:
outlook.exe /safe
4. Disable add-ins  
5. Repair Office installation  
6. Recreate Outlook profile  

## 📝 Model Ticket Note
Outlook failing to launch due to corrupted add-in. Launched in Safe Mode, disabled add-ins, and recreated profile. User confirmed Outlook loading normally. Issue resolved.

