# 🔐 3. Identity Demo – MFA Reset & Re‑Registration

## 🎯 Scenario
User reports:
> “I got a new phone and now I can’t approve MFA prompts.”

## 🔧 Troubleshooting Steps (Demo)
1. Admin Centre → User → Authentication Methods  
2. Remove old phone  
3. Add temporary phone number (if allowed)  
4. Force re‑registration  
5. User signs in → sets up Authenticator app  

## 📝 Model Ticket Note
User unable to receive MFA prompts after device change. Removed old authentication methods and forced re‑registration. User successfully configured new device. Issue resolved.

