# 📁 4. OneDrive Demo – Sync Issues

## 🎯 Scenario
User reports:
> “My OneDrive isn’t syncing and files show a red X.”

## 🔧 Troubleshooting Steps (Demo)
1. Check OneDrive status  
2. Reset OneDrive:
%localappdata%\Microsoft\OneDrive\onedrive.exe /reset
3. Sign out/in  
4. Check file path length  
5. Check storage quota  

## 📝 Model Ticket Note
OneDrive sync corrupted. Reset client and re-authenticated user. Sync resumed successfully. Issue resolved.

