# 🍎 5. macOS Demo – Keychain Password Mismatch

## 🎯 Scenario
User reports:
> “After changing my password, my Mac keeps asking for the old one.”

## 🔧 Troubleshooting Steps (Demo)
1. Open Keychain Access  
2. Search for “Microsoft” and “Exchange”  
3. Delete outdated entries  
4. Restart device  
5. Re-authenticate apps  

## 📝 Model Ticket Note
macOS Keychain storing outdated credentials after password change. Removed old entries and restarted device. User able to sign in normally. Issue resolved.

