# 🛡️ 7. Security Demo – Phishing Email Investigation

## 🎯 Scenario
User reports:
> “I clicked a suspicious link in an email.”

## 🔧 Troubleshooting Steps (Demo)
1. Reset user password  
2. Revoke sessions  
