# 🧠 9. Advanced Scenario – VPN Connected but No Access to Internal Apps

## 🎯 Scenario
User reports:
> “VPN connects but I can’t access the shared drive or internal apps.”

## 🔧 Troubleshooting Steps (Demo)
1. Check routing:
route print
2. Ping internal server  
3. Check DNS suffix  
4. Flush DNS:
ipconfig /flushdns
5. Restart VPN client  

## 📝 Model Ticket Note
VPN connected but internal resources unreachable due to missing DNS suffix. Restarted VPN client and flushed DNS. Access restored.

